      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new? This beauty is in absolute mint condition and has been babied since day one. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person\u2014seriously, not a scratch on it! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see it go, but it\u2019s ready for a new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
