    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2005 Lotus Elise is an uncompromising example of lightweight engineering, featuring an extruded and bonded 6061 aluminum chassis that remains structurally flawless. Powered by the high-revving 1.8L 2ZZ-GE inline-four with VVTL-i, the engine provides a visceral lift transition and linear power delivery to the rear wheels via a close-ratio 6-speed manual transaxle. The suspension geometry is preserved with original Bilstein dampers and Eibach coils, offering telepathic steering feedback through the unassisted rack. This specimen showcases zero composite fatigue, pristine factory paint, and an immaculate interior. It is mechanically sorted with a documented service history, ensuring the AP Racing and Brembo braking systems perform to factory specifications.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Clean title. Original paint. Interior flawless. Mechanically perfect. All service records available. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
